OOC:( OK, Sorry about that. I got the bases mixed up.)

::Battera::

She walked into the small dining hall with CyberShark. She sat down at one 
of the tables. "So, um, what are we to do after this? I mean, uh, do we have 
any orders or any job assigned or anything like that?"
She felt her face plates flush.  She could have smacked herself for that 
one. She knew how stupid that one sounded.  She wanted to go crawl into a 
hole and disappear.

OOC:( Megatron, Scorponok and DarkMouse are at the Destron Base. Megatron is
waiting for Panzertron so they can talk. DarkMouse said that she smelled a
trap while they were all waiting for Panzertron to appear.  Scorponok stayed
with Megatron while DarkMouse went looking around.  The only door she found
open was a CR chamber room.  She was headed back to the room where Megatron
was when she heard a noise behind a door.  She listened and heard nothing so
she porcceded back down the hallway to the room where Megatron and Scorponok
were.)

Wrong base. Magmatron's base is the Destron base.

::CyberShark::

    He looked around and saw that only the hallway was open. "Magmatron,
could you let us in to the Cafeteria? We would like to sit down and have a
meal." He commed to Magmatron.
    "Just a second CyberShark," Magmatron replied. A few seconds later the
door to the cafeteria opened. CyberShark walked in to the medium sized room.
